Package: symTensor
Type: Package
Title: Symmetric Matrix and Tensor Decomposition
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Koki Tsuyuzaki
Maintainer: Koki Tsuyuzaki <k.t.the-answer@hotmail.co.jp>
Description: Provides symmetric matrix and tensor operations and decomposition
    algorithms including symmetric NMF (symNMF), PageRank, Label Propagation,
    Higher-order Power Method, and TOPHITS. Designed to work with rTensor objects.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    rTensor,
    methods,
    stats
Suggests:
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
